{"tid":1296042,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"韓女團MOMOLAND短裙開唱.男粉絲台下自慰被捕","createTime":"2019-07-08T08:37:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T04:25:59.000Z","uid":231132,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e7946e1738a7cd864be507db89f926f14d921ebc","tid":1296042,"uid":231132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T08:37:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdnpuc.sinchew.com.my/pad/pic/2019-07/07/e47ecd71-1aa1-4919-912a-f28d883fe726ea07be87-a3c6-4a0d-a133-ffa79a3c7238.jpg.2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdnpuc.sinchew.com.my%2Fpad%2Fpic%2F2019-07%2F07%2Fe47ecd71-1aa1-4919-912a-f28d883fe726ea07be87-a3c6-4a0d-a133-ffa79a3c7238.jpg.2&h=2871085b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（首爾7日綜合電）以一首洗腦單曲《BBoom BBoom》爆紅的韓國人氣女團MOMOLAND，近日到墨西哥舉辦巡迴見面會，卻因有男粉絲不尊重的舉動，讓其他粉絲氣憤又心疼 ，在推特發起&ldquo;RespectMomoland&rdquo;活動，希望不要再有類似情況發生。<br />\n<br />\n 事緣MOMOLAND在演出當天穿著兩套不同風格服裝，白色連身洋裝性感風和T卹搭牛仔短褲活潑俏皮風，這本該是一場開心的見面會，卻因台下部份男粉不斷叫囂 ，吹口哨說情色話語，還有一名男子竟現場打起手槍，體液噴到前方的女粉絲，雖然最後被警方逮捕，仍讓現場其他粉絲相當氣憤。<br />\n<br />\n 消息在網絡傳開，讓各地粉絲都覺得太過分，沒想到還有人回&ldquo;誰叫她們穿這麼少&rdquo;，讓其他網民氣炸，發起&ldquo;RespectMomoland&rdquo;活動，希望別再發生同樣的事情了。"},{"pid":"485020910b204135252674b0807f8c955019ffa7","tid":1296042,"uid":78018,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T08:39:43.000Z","msg":"有一名男子竟現場打起手槍，體液噴到前方的女粉絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62094d5d4e05afd4c0e7d43d51b54b6e74e763b9","tid":1296042,"uid":165339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T08:39:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://cdnpuc.sinchew.com.my/pad/pic/2019-07/07/e47ecd71-1aa1-4919-912a-f28d883fe726ea07be87-a3c6-4a0d-a133-ffa79a3c7238.jpg.2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdnpuc.sinch